ses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr...\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjn9M7Kt-uTAxU2OLMFHSvoLpNIoOnVuMq0-r5JygEEcQL7MA==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXUyUXAwZzVkcWl4VVluM1J4a2Z0Q3hGcGJ4QXxBQ3Jtc0tsU0NqQTNjVlR1VGZxTDhQd0VTUXBhQjJlZk1jNDRYMzNRVUVPWE1FazBHekh1RnlWYXdrVGFlcFJVbVBLS3FrOFFKeFVnRzRyLVJjRk56aHdfMTltQmtnOWxVaWxDb01JbG9UbmUxQ05DblNwZGNUcw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=SX3ppKcVdKA","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXUyUXAwZzVkcWl4VVluM1J4a2Z0Q3hGcGJ4QXxBQ3Jtc0tsU0NqQTNjVlR1VGZxTDhQd0VTUXBhQjJlZk1jNDRYMzNRVUVPWE1FazBHekh1RnlWYXdrVGFlcFJVbVBLS3FrOFFKeFVnRzRyLVJjRk56aHdfMTltQmtnOWxVaWxDb01JbG9UbmUxQ05DblNwZGNUcw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=SX3ppKcVdKA","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjn9M7Kt-uTAxU2OLMFHSvoLpNIoOnVuMq0-r5JygEEcQL7MA==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWh5VGc1TXRSWnJKQlZ3UGUtOXI2ZlRwSU5JZ3xBQ3Jtc0trQlVWNVg1d1Rl